iginal intent was the wizard evac for groups as their benefit but that is just not a consideration except in rare instances. I ported many a group to planes who just needed me for the ride up. I dont know really. I just know i want to have fun when i log in. I dont want to spend hours and hours  LFG. I dont want to find my areas of available Solo xp nerfed. I dont want to work hard  to earn a skill  only to have it removed. It is &quot;their&quot; game and one of these days i will give it back to them and tell them they can kiss my familiar<br>
